Industry.value: Biotechnology: In Vitro & In Vivo Diagnostic Substances

CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Anbio Biotechnology is dedicated to the advancement of medical technology and the provision of in vitro diagnostics (IVD) products. At Anbio Biotechnology, our extensive portfolio comprises an array of IVD products designed to cater to diverse diagnostic needs. Our comprehensive range encompasses solutions for various applications, including over-the-counter utilization, point-of-care settings, and laboratory applications. Our IVD products are designed to detect a wide range of biomarkers associated with critical medical domains. These domains encompass infectious diseases, cancer, cardiovascular diseases, inflammation, drug abuse, endocrine disorders, renal disease, pharmacogenomics, and diabetes.
